name: Crazy world, flamingo and the birth of a pink hare
description: The newborn is similar to the parents, but is a unique personality. With his unique questions, adventures and challenges. Immediately after birth, an insane world pours on the newborn from all sides. Some situations and meetings will help him in life, but many will create obstacles. What kind of life will a newborn have? Will he win at the end or lose? / 1600x1600px
